reviewText: Very really and to the point.  More graphic than I cared to see but it has a powerful message.
yes this is it. It doesn't get much more real than this. Santorum and all, the wide open chasm of lust and frenzied chemical animal. .Love?

Finally an accurate protray of what meth has done to the gay community. The varying paths we choose in our journey or that the drug chooses for us are here played out with candor and guts.
A must watch for anyone in the gay community who wants to be informed... And more acutely so for those for whose journey meth includes meth.
